sets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實你講既野只係得一個point<br />\n就係資訊唔流通<br />\n第一排既兄弟成日話後面唔退佢地唔會退<br />\n但其實後面好多人都係睇你地頭而決定進退<br />\n前線係be water既形狀決定者，係應該由前線決定幾時退，令到後面既人配合<br />\n而唔係後面退晒先，跟住最前線見到冇人先退"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n本身由西環話退去上環<br />\n係上環又話西環打緊叫我地唔好退去中環住<br />\n咁我咪再行返前囉<br />\n有fd係中環話成班退緊去金鐘 我心諗咁中環咪冇撚晒人?<br />\n第一次條戰線係橫跨幾個地鐵站<br />\n冇乜溝通 希望下次做好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7718e04b4e9112bdc81a61fc978664fa6fcb818","tid":1352963,"uid":70888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ee24b579043821d4227f7a737191614d42c61fd","tid":1352963,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"物資過剩 係違背 be water <br />\n物資多到無人拎，物資站手足想走 都困難，不斷叫人幫手拎，點樣可以快速進退？<br />\n和理非每次肯keep返裝，物資負擔就少好多，自然可以提供返水同糧食，依個係一個改進<br />\n勇武經過咁多次被狗鎮壓，721個日真係打得好靚，有進有退，唔係散沙，真係respect每一位<br />\n我見到721可以改善既位，所以先提出，一齊進步，抗爭先可以更加昇華"},{"pid":"fad18934c8c708a578910b5ea476272e80e89a6a","tid":1352963,"uid":70888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecfca5c3c4212cf0e4b6ff2722945dd1e48a2814","tid":1352963,"uid":243834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:53:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n裝備真係要重用！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:50:25.000Z","msg":"啲人覺得唔洗錢同埋無諗過物資手足既負擔<br />\n我見到佢地都辛苦，同埋運送咁大量物資風險唔細"},{"pid":"7ea77a5d488b625f7dde869f99df3c915b7f7048","tid":1352963,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e6506cdc1df5ef0796522366aad3f18b029de43","tid":1352963,"uid":243834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"866eabe6bae9bcc69688b221fe30d1d9d250b081","tid":1352963,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2c256f8daa955ddf040f8c5a173dc880ba43b40c","tid":1352963,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:47:55.000Z","msg":"軍師你去一次前線就知<br />\n願意企頭排嘅人真係唔多<br />\n當日眼罩安全帽多到要派<br />\n依然好多人係唔拎 和理非look行黎行去/坐<br />\n反而企前果啲6 7點已經full gear<br />\n<br />\n下次需要嘅係水同食物<br />\n知道買裝備送去前線嘅巴絲好有心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"五毛只要你試過一次唔夠裝備就唔撚會敢講呢d 野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:54:48.000Z","msg":"其實如果有心去做，自己點解唔整裝要到時攞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"同意，有心既人基本上自備晒<br />\n而無心既，亦都唔會諗住上前線<br />\n見到最多既 係人拎佢又拎，走既時候就棄晒"},{"pid":"aab901a9fdaf64be9e2907afdb3dba1797ac9075","tid":1352963,"uid":1297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"水同食物係人必需品<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次真係好缺"},{"pid":"5c87ffa130cc2aef1b63f9a24f9a490b32c6d78d","tid":1352963,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f9aa9fab770ec03c9dd7e3112412dae055c0cbb","tid":1352963,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n到新聞話上環放左催淚彈，我發夢就由中環走返過去，但沿途真係好多好多手足坐晒係度，有唔少係著左裝，其實你地擔唔擔心上環班手足？去到上環前線真係唔多人，係去到後期先多返，我知道大家都好攰，但前線手足要人既時候 可唔可起身一齊行過去？？我一個人走返去上環，但見住成班人坐係度，個心情真係唔識形容。。 <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣我就坐左係後面既<br />\n本身我就係中聯辦<br />\n後尾話散水就一直走<br />\n<br />\n走到後面我已經唔太知前面咩事<br />\n<br />\n有人話出催淚彈我根本唔知係打算撤定想推，但又有物資傳返落黎，但未走曬我又唔想走<br />\n所以就一直係中環守，諗住有事就上返去<br />\n到後尾有人話要支援就成班人上返去<br />\n<br />\n我覺得係情況太亂，大家唔知應該做乜所以先咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"係，消息太亂，因為條線太長"},{"pid":"9890339debbb9707ac729e15bee22fbc570a83f7","tid":1352963,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989c0436700fdf07963ace6ee443d6bedaa5800e","tid":1352963,"uid":8948,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a51bcde0b18a671d9ba9e8ca6bc3a41351afa49f","tid":1352963,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"原來睇返自己寫左好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係tldr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實你講既野只係得一個point<br />\n就係資訊唔流通<br />\n第一排既兄弟成日話後面唔退佢地唔會退<br />\n但其實後面好多人都係睇你地頭而決定進退<br />\n前線係be water既形狀決定者，係應該由前線決定幾時退，令到後面既人配合<br />\n而唔係後面退晒先，跟住最前線見到冇人先退"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實都有提到要改善既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ba82be54cd5cd06f4705ba4501407705edc3cc","tid":1352963,"uid":50762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"真係好浪費 次次大家都放低哂啲野走<br />\n其實真係要錢架<br />\n同埋自備gear啦屌"},{"pid":"0b2692771112ad3bb7daa203e16125ce7c766554","tid":1352963,"uid":201427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:12:13.000Z","msg":"有少少提外話<br />\n721同612唔同係根本中環有好多人<br />\n但唔知上環開緊戰<br />\n成班坐係到以為風平浪靜<br />\n應該好似612咁搵多d哨兵叫人上前"},{"pid":"e38a50bc2a3ae6cef058a876239aea789842480c","tid":1352963,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支持前線所有決定</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n民情，輿論，選票，呢啲唔洗我哋去諗，點去收拾所謂嘅殘局，就交比啲政治人物去煩啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋要做嘅係我哋認為啱嘅事</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LYjFvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LYjFvR.jpg&h=d444c005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<code>「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）</code><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求，勿忘初衷\n遍地開花，不撤不散\n打倒軍權，反對國家恐怖主義\n光復香港，時代革命\n\n\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序\n二、收回612暴動定性\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n定性721黑警上環血腥鎮壓，元朗黑社會恐怖襲擊，警黑合作散播國家恐怖主義:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察戰線:</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gq6kYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gq6kYx.jpg&h=1f5648e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hY7P3bT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhY7P3bT.jpg&h=5c1777d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警察冇預警下開槍射36發橡膠彈，有人爆頭，警察已無視通例，已失去合法性<br />\n警察放任黑社會打市民，完全冇制止，並假指無發現武器收隊，傳媒發現雙方實有公開溝通<br />\n警察公然無視電話求助，元朗警署落閘，違反警隊職責<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑社會戰線:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7DWJcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7DWJcw.jpg&h=92c6a934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idEKR5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidEKR5S.jpg&h=e6380dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉攏任何政治冷感市民，有錢人，元朗問題非個別事件，收錢恐襲任何區都會發生，任何人都有機會中招<br />\n俾藍絲睇到佢地支持何君堯即係支持黑社會打人斬人，令藍絲同何君堯反面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際戰線:</span><br />\n向外國抗議中國政府散播國家恐怖主義<br />\n向外媒及各國投訴香港警察包庇黑社會合作各自無差別打人，違反通例無預警開槍，已失去合法性<br />\n港鐵作為國際地鐵聯盟之一公然妄顧市民安危強逼市民離開車廂被打<br />\n黑社會涉嫌在元朗發動恐襲襲擊，主腦直指中共政府<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自發治安戰線:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sf52DMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsf52DMn.jpg&h=ecc7650f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OejSgx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOejSgx3.jpg&h=01748b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港防衛隊  正式成立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342844</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n強烈建議各區組織民衛隊，取代黑警職責<br />\n<br />\n【HKSDF】香港自衛隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352390</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【元朗恐襲】真心，如果眾籌，成立「香港自衛隊保安公司」優先過登報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346745\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346745</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵戰線:</span><br />\n全面係所有車站招貼: 元朗站逼市民落車被打，妄顧安危<br />\n一定要令每個站每個角落都見到<br />\n全面不合作運動，再加宣傳市民全面罷坐港鐵<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>唔好再比政府帶風向啦，元朗恐襲完個個第二日正正常常返工有冇搞錯呀，仲要出面一個行動post都冇！由今日起要令交通癱瘓，救救香港唔該</code><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 有痴線佬係地鐵裸跑導致延誤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351224\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351224</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n經過今日我發現左幾個問題：<br />\n1.我地既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標係要停哂成架列車，唔係拖延架車</span></span>，目標係要停列<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>推到上報</strong></span></span>，咁打工仔先可以大條道理咁講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇車返唔到工</span></span>，報都推唔到既話只會令大家覺得令到佢地遲到，到時會開始屌返我地轉頭，所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到時候亦都需要做文宣係咁airdrop</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 人手太散太易比人捉，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中返係幾個點</span></span>就好了，唔係既話好容易比人屌走，唔好再攞阻到幾次門打飛機<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港人真係太多包袱太驚返唔到工比人屌，直接令到響應人數唔夠而呢場運動未有很成功。但係我想講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">返唔到工大家都有份，想返唔到工就要大家一齊做，唔好等人幫你做</span></span>。當每個人都一齊響應令交通癱瘓既時候就唔會有返工遲到既出現，係返唔到工。<br />\n<br />\n3. 太多人去到之後怕左就暈唔到，點都要有一個人開始架啦，香港人就係咁，乜都好驚，所以你有啲膽既話不妨第一個唔舒服。就好似今日大圍咁令大家都重點果種火。<br />\n<br />\n頂門呢啲真係唔好做啦，因為頂門頂唔到幾多次，都阻唔到好耐。<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔小心跌左野入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔小心跌咗嘢入路軌</span></span>，跌左火機果啲就唔好啦，不過跌左一定要同職員講，唔係好危險<br />\n<br />\n2. 見到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人唔舒服要拉緊急制停車</span></span>，冇計人命關天，一卡有五隻，拉哂佢，拉埋格離果卡都仲得，唔洗同佢客氣<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔小心<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">整壞架車是但一道門</span></span>，就成架車都唔用得，情況就好似琴日九龍塘咁，成條線delay十幾分鐘<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經過恐襲大家變哂痴線佬落哂路軌</span></span>，跑又好叫又好<br />\n<br />\n大家都係係地鐵唔舒服姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n三罷交癱tg link</strong></span></span>:<br />\n<br />\n大group:<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mtr723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtr723&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=5ef8248a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/mtr723</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1HDsPqChixQv4i2Yw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP1HDsPqChixQv4i2Yw&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=561bb946\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1HDsPqChixQv4i2Yw</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1AfZbR7xvsS0C6h4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP1AfZbR7xvsS0C6h4A&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=3c24f1e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1AfZbR7xvsS0C6h4A</a><br />\n<br />\n港島綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP0jHZcU9BYIAXhEFWw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP0jHZcU9BYIAXhEFWw&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=ef511234\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP0jHZcU9BYIAXhEFWw</a><br />\n<br />\n東鐵綫<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1iH0REZYKW6RDSItw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FH9HhP1iH0REZYKW6RDSItw&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjeQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=535ca943\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1iH0REZYKW6RDSItw</a><br />\n<br />\n西